Name: Puzzletronics Digital Infinite
About the game: Puzzletronics Digital Infinite is a minimalist puzzle in the style of jigsaw. The player must move pieces to form logical circuits while listening to a calm and relaxing soundtrack. Challenge yourself through 133 different levels and with varying levels of difficulty, knowing the behavior of logic gates and digital logic. Characteristics: More than 130 Different levels and with random pieces arrangement. Calm and relaxing soundtrack. Minimalist and colorful environment. Lots of different pieces.
